_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user

# NCrunch
_NCrunch_*
.NCrunch_*
.*crunch*.local.xml
nCrunchTemp_*

# CodeRush personal settings
**/.cr/personal

